assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咁多先，希望樓主真係好好守承諾，<br />\n唔好再上黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530df034bf3ddc2f0505f5512895b7371b1e0a5e","tid":237193,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:13:19.000Z","msg":"得罪全世界呀你呢家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n口臭唔洗付出代價呀？！"},{"pid":"8935bc90350bc27c77c7f5a9fadea96bae07b910","tid":237193,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:33:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>條賤種拎強姦慘劇黎講笑<br />\n聲稱要合法化強姦十點後外出嘅女人</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/237323/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/237323/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n你喺網上唔代表可以乜都講<br />\n你上得連登就代表你係一個人<br />\n唔該你地似返個人<br />\n認撚住條雞蟲份人係幾撚低劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407d63d0f55f7f8b9dccfb113829746367372166","tid":237193,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:34:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>支那仔被人撚狗撚到 1001 POST</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/219567/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/219567/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n潮文都作埋<br />\n<br />\n點解入十連 post?<br />\n巴閉囉 爆 post 主義 推 post<br />\n我唔妥你 可以斷你<br />\n我唔鐘意你 可以恥笑你<br />\n𡃁仔你啤咩呀 出黎十連吖<br />\n十連呀<br />\n連我吖 連吖<br />\n我連你 你連我 點呀<br />\n你見過鯨大校舍未，你見過米八男神未呀<br />\n你話嫐巴係你偶像吖嘛 你見過嫐巴未<br />\n十連 post 揸 fit 人吖嘛 好巴閉呀 ?<br />\n你知唔知佢個 post 俾人騎劫掹唔到<br />\n你知唔知佢親眼睇住佢癲咗，佢醫唔到<br />\n你知唔知嫐巴諗緊咩呀?<br />\n話俾你聽佢唔想做揸fit人<br />\n佢唔想開十連 post<br />\n但係佢無辦法 無得返轉頭<br />\n係呀 每個人都有偶像 我都有<br />\n其實 十唔十連 我理唔到咁多<br />\n但係我想話俾你聽 開錯 post 無得返轉頭㗎"},{"pid":"c1928ae097584b37c36d608db3cb95b4863cb4e2","tid"